%TMPL:DEF{"heading"}%More Actions on Topic [[%TOPIC%]]%TMPL:END%
%TMPL:DEF{"message"}%

   * *Delete topic:*
      * *<a href="%SCRIPTURLPATH%/rename%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%?newweb=%TRASHWEB%&amp;nonwikiword=on" rel='nofollow'>Delete topic...</a>*,
        looking for references in _all public webs_ &nbsp; *(recommended)*
      * <a href="%SCRIPTURLPATH%/rename%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%?newweb=%TRASHWEB%&amp;nonwikiword=on&amp;currentwebonly=on" rel='nofollow'>Delete topic...</a>,
        looking for references in _%WEB% web_ only

   * *Rename or move topic:*
      * *<a href="%SCRIPTURLPATH%/rename%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%" rel='nofollow'>Rename/move topic...</a>*,
        looking for references in _all public webs_ &nbsp; *(recommended)*
      * <a href="%SCRIPTURLPATH%/rename%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%?currentwebonly=on" rel='nofollow'>Rename/move topic...</a>,
        looking for references in _%WEB% web_ only

   * *Backlinks:*
      * Find topics <a href="%SCRIPTURLPATH%/oops%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%?template=backlinksweb" title="Search all webs for topics that link to here" accesskey="w">in <nop>%WEB% <span class="patternAccessKey">w</span>eb</a> that link to <nop>%TOPIC%
      * Find topics <a href="%SCRIPTURLPATH%/oops%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%?template=backlinksallwebs" title="Search the <nop>%WEB% Web for topics that link to here" accesskey="l">in a<span class="patternAccessKey">ll</span> public webs</a> that link to <nop>%TOPIC%

   * *Child topics in <nop>%WEB% web:*
      * %METASEARCH{type="parent" web="%WEB%" topic="%TOPIC%" default="No child topics"}%

<form name="main" action="%EDITURL%">
   * *Set new topic parent:*
      * Step 1: Select topic parent: %BR%
        <select name="topicparent" size="10">
        <option value="none">none (remove topic parent)</option>
        %TOPICLIST{"<option value=$qname>$name</option>" separator=" "}%
        </select>
      * Step 2: Continue to <input type="submit" class="twikiSubmit" value="Edit" /> and save <nop>%TOPIC% to activate the new parent
        <input type="hidden" name="t" value="%SERVERTIME{$year$mo$day$hour$min$sec}%" />
</form>

<form name="main" action="%SCRIPTURLPATH%/view%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%">
   * *View previous topic revision:*
      * Revision: <input type="text" name="rev" size="6" value="%PARAM2%" />
        in <input type="checkbox" class="twikiCheckbox" id="raw" name="raw" /><label for="raw">raw text format</label>
        <input type="submit" class="twikiSubmit" value="View revision" />
      * Revisions: 1.1 ... %PARAM1%
</form>

<form name="main" action="%SCRIPTURLPATH%/rdiff%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%">
   * *Compare revisions:*
      * Older revision:&nbsp;&nbsp; <input type="text" name="rev2" size="6" value="1.1" />
      * Newer revision: <input type="text" name="rev1" size="6" value="%PARAM1%" />
        <input type="submit" class="twikiSubmit" value="View difference" />
</form>

   * *Edit topic preference settings:*
      * <a href="%SCRIPTURLPATH%/manage%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%?action=editSettings" rel='nofollow'>Edit settings</a> for this topic %TMPL:END%
